  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effects of Pilates method and aerobic training in hypertensive
      subjects. Half of participants will be trained with Pilates, while the other half will be
      trained with aerobic exercise during 8 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
